Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.10,0:00:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人要來了哦快打掃一下,     知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.14,0:00:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股好像又大了    沒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.34,0:00:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦不可能啦   也是哦  我量一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.39,0:00:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉過去吧    把裙子撩起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.57,0:00:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,93啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.74,0:00:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然大了哦   來的時候不到90    是嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.11,0:00:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.35,0:01:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊    難道是被看著的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.64,0:01:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡女僕的工作   終于可以如願了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.78,0:02:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個婦人已經去世的家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.65,0:02:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個女人哦 每天都在加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.91,0:02:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是包括男主人都在看屁股呢  這是不是也是女僕的作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.59,0:02:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何我一定會成為   优秀的女僕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.33,0:02:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又大了哦'
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓我看一下啊  是的啦   屁股嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難为情啦   沒事的啦   看看而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.16,0:03:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翘起來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.56,0:03:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.54,0:03:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛   多大了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.73,0:03:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只是屁股變大阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.97,0:04:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊   麼回事啊   難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.32,0:04:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人   對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.03,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛打扫了一半哦    這個·不用管啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.28,0:04:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任性奉献大屁股的女仆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刺激啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.05,0:06:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.46,0:06:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳不好把屁股露出來哦   實在是汰壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.01,0:07:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有想這樣啦     不要這麼闻了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.29,0:07:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快洗碗啊    沒有見我说话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.34,0:07:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子我不好洗碗的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.74,0:07:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦   快繼繬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.64,0:08:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊   怎么不洗啊   對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.01,0:08:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先不洗了   吧坐到我臉上嘴那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把水關了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股快坐上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.21,0:09:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎    對了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.71,0:09:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快压哦   這樣啦    這樣嗎,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.61,0:10:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膝蓋跪下來吧   坐下來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.78,0:11:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都鼓起來了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.66,0:11:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快压下來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.11,0:11:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.01,0:12:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫了吧直接坐下來吧  快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.69,0:12:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.45,0:13:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地動哦    這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续压哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.67,0:14:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要自己爽哦也讓我也爽嘛   對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快擠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.53,0:15:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先起來讓大肉棒爽一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.24,0:15:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎   快擠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.79,0:16:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴濕了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.73,0:16:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦   為什麼濕了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.31,0:16:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己摸吧   讓我欣赏一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了我的大肉棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.67,0:16:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難為情阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.64,0:16:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就喜歡看妳害羞的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.29,0:17:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己摸感覺怎麼樣阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.67,0:17:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽啊    爽了啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.65,0:18:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了淫荡的声音了哦  对不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.60,0:18:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗 好爽阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.04,0:18:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太爽了啦  要晕了啦   那让我看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.92,0:19:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦    只知道自己爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.46,0:19:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦   讓我也爽一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.38,0:19:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塗點唾液上去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.59,0:19:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢點擠哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.67,0:20:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓我爽哦·  好的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.11,0:20:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽啊   看著大屁股好兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難為情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.23,0:20:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我興奮是不是很高兴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.80,0:20:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.64,0:20:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.05,0:20:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽嗎   越來越爽了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.93,0:21:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著大屁股忍不住了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.33,0:21:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出來了哦   射了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.64,0:21:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.22,0:21:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.04,0:21:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大屁股讓你興奮了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.74,0:22:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽啊   我好高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.28,0:22:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了吧  什麼時候能洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.36,0:22:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦   馬上就好哦    剛才就說可以了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.69,0:22:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人真的對不起哦  这样没办法成为合格的女仆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.80,0:23:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦   沒有反省哦  給我好好反省哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.61,0:23:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.88,0:23:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手拿开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.29,0:23:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.64,0:23:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都濕了  啦這樣不好啦  不用管啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.68,0:23:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.71,0:23:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什麼吗 這樣不行哦    主人不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.92,0:23:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会做好的啦   嘴还怎么硬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.37,0:24:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道不想成為合格的女仆吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.98,0:24:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.48,0:24:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了  我好好教教你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.59,0:24:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.63,0:24:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.44,0:24:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗表情阿   這是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.48,0:24:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為合格女僕的精油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.49,0:25:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想成合格女僕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.84,0:25:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也要弄濕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.48,0:25:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦   好難為情啊    說什麼廢話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.69,0:25:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為誰服務啊  說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.19,0:25:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了主人啦    那就絕對服从我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.77,0:25:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉過去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.80,0:25:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉過去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.98,0:25:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有屁越來越大哦  對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.15,0:26:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面有成为女仆的知识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.80,0:26:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面肯定有有用的知识哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.48,0:26:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:31.55,0:26:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿了这样的内裤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:35.29,0:26:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有說過穿吧  是的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.23,0:26:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己私自穿得嗎   是的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.54,0:26:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.01,0:27:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸這麼大了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.52,0:27:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼反應啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.29,0:27:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼反應啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.33,0:27:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼反應啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.11,0:27:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼这么硬阿   我怎麼啦      是你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.69,0:27:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么啦   是你摸了所以才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.96,0:27:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不能摸嗎  不是的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:52.00,0:27:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.90,0:27:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不能這樣摸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:01.14,0:28:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.91,0:28:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起主人   是我淫蕩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.75,0:28:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛   是妳淫樣才这样的啊   對不起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.86,0:28:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我绕了妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.81,0:28:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这样吗  讨厌吗  不讨厌的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.33,0:29:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那用這個吧   会更加加淫荡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.14,0:29:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:08.34,0:29:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了哦    拜託了啦   再說一次阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:19.35,0:29:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個淫荡的女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:28.46,0:29:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個淫蕩的女人哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:37.84,0:29:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真能說這樣的话哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:03.80,0:30:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有哪儿會有感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.71,0:30:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在听着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.51,0:30:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有屁股啦   聽不見哦  是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.29,0:30:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.56,0:30:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什啊  喜欢被虐待啊   不要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:43.77,0:30:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被我看著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.44,0:30:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說就停了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:13.67,0:31:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.54,0:31:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這個哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:28.18,0:31:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂起來哦   對了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:01.41,0:32:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰核在哪裡啊
